track_notes:
NOTE: G(W)8TMV told me 8 years after my activation that this track is no good - you may prefer to make your own way and ignore my guidance. 

It was hard to find the path in snow, so the walk up was on rough ground. Return route was slightly longer but easier walking, mostly on a track and path. Visibility was poor and the summit as far as we could see was featureless and without cover.
track_title: From top car park of Big Pit MIning Museam

track_notes: Total time (including ops): 1hr 40m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards.
